description: This operation provides all the locations that are available for resource providers; however, each resource provider may support a subset of this list.

displayname.description: The display name of the location.

api_version.description: The API version to use for the operation.

id.description: The fully qualified ID of the location. For example, /subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/locations/westus.
